msgid ""
"The system automatically blocks students from taking credits (SKS) exceeding"
" their GPA limit, and prevents registration if the class capacity is full. "
"No more manual administrative leniency."
msgstr ""
"Sistem secara otomatis memblokir mahasiswa untuk mengambil SKS (SKS) yang "
"melebihi batas IPK, dan mencegah pendaftaran jika kapasitas kelas sudah "
"penuh. Tidak ada lagi keringanan administratif manual."

#. module: campus_core
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_core.core_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"The system detects class schedule conflict (Time Overlap) in real-time when "
"students compile their KRS, ensuring students do not choose two classes at "
"the same time."
msgstr ""
"Sistem mendeteksi konflik jadwal kelas (Time Overlap) secara real-time pada "
"saat siswa menyusun KRS, sehingga siswa tidak memilih dua kelas dalam waktu "
"yang bersamaan."

#. module: campus_core
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_core.core_homepage_docs
