"                            The system is designed with Odoo's modular architecture, implementing Python ORM automation, comprehensive business validation, and layered security systems."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini memuat spesifikasi teknis dan Standard Operating Procedure (SOP) Educational Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP).\n"
